name: Frida Punk 019 - Once Bitten Twice Shy
description: Fun fact: Frida and Diego Rivera were married twice. Once in 1929 after which they were divorced in a brief time and again 1940. They had a turbulent relationship, suspected to have infidelity on both sides and Fridas works:  "Self-Portrait as Tehunana" and "Diego and I," are said to be testaments to their troublesome and controversial relationship.
